Second dose of COVID vaccine injected to Levies personnel in Levies line.Those who are eligible for vaccine are requested to get vaccinated.There isn’t any harm in getting vaccinated.

A surprise visit of BHU GoR colony was conducted. Staff was present & strict compliance of COVID-19 SOPs was ensured, while the missing facilities were noted & further recommended to the concerned authorities.
